    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，在关税后果，“政策永远不会改变”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-says-policies-will-never-change-amid-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他的经济政策“将永远不会改变”，因为他的全面关税继续对全球经济造成严重破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-says-policies-will-never-change-amid-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部权衡使公司鄙视的惩罚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/doj-weighs-getting-rid-of-a-punishment-that-companies-despise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[司法部正在权衡是否将公司从雇用外部监视器的义务中释放，这是与检察官的定居点的一部分。长期以来一直挫败高管的一种监督形式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/doj-weighs-getting-rid-of-a-punishment-that-companies-despise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普征收取代美国国会支持的非洲贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-tariffs-to-supersede-us-congress-backed-africa-trade-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对美国大多数贸易伙伴的关税将破坏一项25年历史的协议，这使许多最贫穷的非洲国家无义务与世界上最大的经济体接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-tariffs-to-supersede-us-congress-backed-africa-trade-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 11:36:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲁贝尼在特朗普变成“理性”之前看到了更多的市场下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/roubini-sees-more-market-declines-before-trump-turns-rational</link>
      <description><![CDATA[努里尔·鲁贝尼（Nouriel Roubini）预测，随着美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）拨打他的全球贸易攻击，股市更正可能会加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/roubini-sees-more-market-declines-before-trump-turns-rational</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 11:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业突然突击，因为共和党权重限制公司盐中断</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/businesses-pounce-as-gop-weighs-limiting-corporate-salt-break</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商业团体正在动员共和党人之间的计划收集势头，以减少大量使用的联邦所得税减免，从而使公司能够扣除州和地方税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/businesses-pounce-as-gop-weighs-limiting-corporate-salt-break</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称法国对极右翼领导人的审判为“女巫狩猎”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-calls-france-s-trial-of-far-right-leader-a-witch-hunt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）敦促欧洲公司在华盛顿的贸易战中停留在美国的投资仅几个小时后，就在法国四面楚歌的极右翼领导人身后投掷了他的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-calls-france-s-trial-of-far-right-leader-a-witch-hunt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:36:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非警惕对我们征收互惠贸易关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/south-africa-wary-of-imposing-reciprocal-trade-tariffs-on-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非政府表示，在华盛顿以惩罚性指控击中该惩罚后，急于向美国进口征收互惠关税，这将是不适的和适得其反的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/south-africa-wary-of-imposing-reciprocal-trade-tariffs-on-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 10:36:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大欧洲呼吁普京回应美国停火计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-canada-call-on-putin-to-respond-to-us-ceasefire-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的欧洲盟友和加拿大敦促俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）立即回应美国基辅（Kyiv）在没有条件的情况下接受的部分停火提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-canada-call-on-putin-to-respond-to-us-ceasefire-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列陆军搬进北加拿大，加大对哈马斯的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/israeli-army-moves-into-north-gaza-to-increase-pressure-on-hamas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列已将士兵送入加沙北部的部分地区，称其想扩大对阵哈马斯的行动，在那里扩展一个缓冲区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/israeli-army-moves-into-north-gaza-to-increase-pressure-on-hamas</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 06:15:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南寻求三个月的关税延迟以允许谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南已要求特朗普政府持有其计划的46％对进口越南产品的关税，最多三个月，以实现进一步的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
